Create a New Sheet → Rename it as "Dashboard".
Insert a Title:
Click A1, type "Amazon Sales Dashboard 2024", and apply:
Bold Font
Merge & Center
Font Size: 18+
Add KPI Summary Cards:
Create three cards for:
Total Sales (₹)
Total Units Sold
Number of Cities
Use formulas:
excel
Copy
Edit
=SUM(SalesData!H:H)   // Total Sales Calculation
=SUM(SalesData!G:G)   // Total Units Sold
=COUNTA(UNIQUE(SalesData!J:J)) // Count Cities
Apply borders, colors, and bold text for clarity.
